---
title: Pulled Beef & Vegetable Stew with Parmesan Mash
description: You've tried pulled pork. Now it's time to give our tender and tasty pulled beef a go! From the rich tomato stew infused with rosemary to the creamy mash and delightful sautéed greens, don't be too surprised if the bowls are left licked clean!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pulled-beef-vegetable-stew-09bf2c75.jpg
